OL,5, Disposable vapes cause litter problems,
OL,6, are a fire hazard and appeal too       
OL,7, strongly to children, according to     
OL,8, local councils in England and Wales.   
OL,10,FThe Local Government Association says  
OL,11,F1.3m vapes are thrown away each week   
OL,12,Fand wants them banned by 2024.         
OL,14,FSingle use varieties have surged in    
OL,15,Fpopularity, driven by Chinese brands   
OL,16,Fsuch as Elfbar and Lost Mary.          
OL,18,FThe UK Vaping Industry Association says
OL,19,Fthey help smokers quit and can be      
OL,20,Frecycled.                              
